法廷　🈡（８）向き合う覚悟","description":"結城（小木茂光）は、精神科医・山路（和久井映見）に何かを伝えようとしていた。その事実を知った安堂（松山ケンイチ）は、結城が残した手がかりをもとに、前橋一家殺人事件との接点を探り始める。安堂の精神状態を案じた小野崎（鳴海唯）は調査に同行。前橋地裁第一支部、弁護団、検察がそれぞれの立場から真相に迫る中、真犯人の存在が浮かび上がり、徐々に点と点がつながっていく。そしてついに、再審請求の決議の日を迎える。","url":"https://www.web.nhk/tv/an/drama-themis/pl/series-tep-32VWPKM6NX/ep/J65M4J33WP","identifierGroup":{"environmentId":"hskOriginal","broadcastEventId":"g1-130-2026031012164","serviceId":"g1","streamType":"vod"},"detailedContentStatus":{"environmentId":"hskOriginal","streamType":"vod","contentStatus":"notyet"},"detailedVideoDescriptor":"https://simul.hsk.st.nhk/npd3/7fe0-0400/20260310/2f84-1-1-b4569581d478a9e7e9ae240ceeda2bf4/videoinfo-7f2fe6b7ea445e40d1cd558e6f4872da.json","expires":"2026-03-17T22:44:30+09:00","duration":"PT44M30S","startDate":"2026-03-10T22:00:00+09:00","endDate":"2026-03-10T22:44:30+09:00","isDivided":false,"publication":[{"id":"g1-130-2026031012164","url":"https://api-local.ss.org.nhk/r8/t/broadcastevent/be/g1-130-2026031012164.json","isLiveBroadcast":true}],"uploadDate":"2026-03-10T22:44:30+09:00"}],"citation":[],"detailedPinnedCitation":[],"sameAs":[],"correction":[],"url":"https://api-local.ss.org.nhk/r8/t/tvepisode/te/J65M4J33WP.json","canonical":"https://www.web.nhk/tv/an/drama-themis/pl/series-tep-32VWPKM6NX/ep/J65M4J33WP","associatedMedia":[{"id":"bcUploadTrailer1","name":"【ドラマ10】テミスの不確かな法廷","description":"(8)向き合う覚悟\n","embedUrl":"https://www.nhk.jp/assets/players/bc/v3/index.html?account=6415847969001&player=YVUjvvMQb&videoId=6390301977112","identifierGroup":{"environmentId":"bcUploadTrailer","streamType":"clip","bcAccountId":"6415847969001","bcVideoId":"6390301977112"},"detailedContentStatus":{"environmentId":"bcUploadTrailer","streamType":"clip","contentStatus":"ready"},"thumbnail":{"main":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/J65M4J33WP/J65M4J33WP-eyecatch_8d2915ea19e98262113db0d7843af8cd.png","width":1920,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/t