1b:["$","$Lb","series-tep-P52L88MYXY",{"spacing":"paragraph","children":[["$","$L10",null,{"title":"大河ドラマ「豊臣兄弟！」","link":{"href":"https://www.web.nhk/tv/an/toyotomi-kyodai/pl/series-tep-P52L88MYXY"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"itemWidth":{"mobile":171,"desktop":304},"children":[["$","$L12","V79QN34LZ7",{"content":{"type":"TVEpisode","id":"V79QN34LZ7","name":"(9)竹中半兵衛という男","detailedEpisodeNameRuby":"","identifierGroup":{"tvEpisodeId":"V79QN34LZ7","tvSeriesId":"P52L88MYXY","tvEpisodeName":"(9)竹中半兵衛という男","tvSeriesName":"大河ドラマ「豊臣兄弟！」","hashtag":[],"siteId":"8969","serviceId":["g1","g2","s1","s2","s5"],"aliasId":"toyotomi-kyodai","formatGenreTag":[{"id":"03","name":"ドラマ"}],"themeGenreTag":[{"id":"031","name":"国内ドラマ"},{"id":"033","name":"時代劇"}]},"keyword":[],"description":"直（白石聖）の死を悼む間もないまま、小一郎（仲野太賀）は美濃国主・斎藤龍興（濱田龍臣）の家臣、竹中半兵衛（菅田将暉）の調略に向かう。だが知恵者と名高い半兵衛は相当の変わり者で、小一郎と藤吉郎（池松壮亮）は翻弄される。その一方で、２人は斎藤家重臣・安藤守就（田中哲司）から思わぬ申し出を受ける。兄弟の報告を聞いた信長（小栗旬）は龍興の居城を包囲するも、窮地の龍興の前に半兵衛があらわれる。","dateCreated":"2026-02-02T18:24:06+09:00","dateModified":"2026-03-02T15:37:41+09:00","actor":[{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"29D4D7A7-E3F2-4E1F-94CA-046080070DC0","wikidataId":"Q11444506"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"仲野 太賀","detailedNameRuby":"なかの たいが","familyName":"仲野","givenName":"太賀","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"なかの","detailedGivenNameRuby":"たいが","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_2e4f43bc990dfaa6d4477eded7ef370a.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_23f990abd5ef3e1f02468ff2e9fe7fc5.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_0a9515dff6449441235f861779b8ea9b.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"小一郎（豊臣秀長）","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"こいちろう（とよとみ ひでなが）","description":"天下人・豊臣秀吉の弟\n登場時の名は小一郎。兄の天下取りをいちずに支え続けた「天下一の補佐役」といわれている。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"D690F0C8-05B8-4A71-9A1E-13B8A756E70D","wikidataId":"Q1058963"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"池松 壮亮","detailedNameRuby":"いけまつ そうすけ","familyName":"池松","givenName":"壮亮","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"いけまつ","detailedGivenNameRuby":"そうすけ","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_4f93e5276609f6f43e9c328f965eb6e6.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_3d74da780b5e535b14406469f0191f93.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_64c55d28509ee3a35e5bb0f5858e4fbe.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"藤吉郎（豊臣秀吉）","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"とうきちろう（とよとみ ひでよし）","description":"小一郎を乱世に巻き込んだ野心家の兄\n小一郎の３歳年上の兄。登場時の名は藤吉郎。尾張中村の貧しい農家で生まれ育ったが、主君である戦国武将・織田信長のもとでメキメキと頭角をあらわし、ついには天下統一を果たす。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"00110902-AE66-45F8-B48D-E45DBA3F0CA8","wikidataId":"Q48758750"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"白石 聖","detailedNameRuby":"しらいし せい","familyName":"白石","givenName":"聖","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"しらいし","detailedGivenNameRuby":"せい","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_1baa2df91b7e56ba54ecfb1fc0c04e54.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_3f071e3e5ed5e23b96fa64ecda80c327.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_2bc62bb524ef23de605f03a3a81f1416.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"直","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"なお","description":"小一郎の幼なじみ“初恋のひと”\n小一郎と藤吉郎の故郷である尾張中村の土豪の娘。小一郎と同い年の幼なじみ。男勝りな性格だが、小一郎のことをひそかに慕っている。乱世に翻弄される悲劇のヒロイン。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"66D5AA5D-8A64-4B6A-ABB7-5292F551EB64","wikidataId":"Q456644"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"坂井 真紀","detailedNameRuby":"さかい まき","familyName":"坂井","givenName":"真紀","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"さかい","detailedGivenNameRuby":"まき","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_030c8f28b7f69208f483416301aac507.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_5e87375cf8fc37c56250f9de49c08681.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_98381a29ef693f26527b144c8bc8163a.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"なか","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"","description":"息子たちの出世を温かく見守る母\n豊臣兄弟の母。夫を早くに亡くし、女手一つで二男二女を育てる。息子たちの異例の出世に喜びやとまどいを感じながらも温かく見守り、天下人となった秀吉が関白に就任すると「大政所（おおまんどころ）」と称されるようになる。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"95D8852C-551F-4464-8309-F469B5AF370F","wikidataId":"Q11347265"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"宮澤 エマ","detailedNameRuby":"みやざわ えま","familyName":"宮澤","givenName":"エマ","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"みやざわ","detailedGivenNameRuby":"えま","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_9dfd7373097fcf7237f5e525bdc94a2b.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_915e601e5be54b8ecf5c759c43ae0b77.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_73e1fe6b5ffb2c0114c269e55f92c237.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"とも","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"","description":"兄弟に厳しくあたるしっかり者の姉\n豊臣兄弟の姉。しっかり者で負けん気が強い。三人の男児を産み育てるが、跡継ぎに恵まれなかった弟の秀吉によって政治の道具として利用される。のちに秀吉の後継者となった長男の秀次は謀反の疑いをかけられ妻子とともに処刑されることになる。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"66A58515-7387-4FA8-8F8C-FF4388E0CF59","wikidataId":"Q11432413"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"大倉 孝二","detailedNameRuby":"おおくら こうじ","familyName":"大倉","givenName":"孝二","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"おおくら","detailedGivenNameRuby":"こうじ","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_3a34fdeff5f7369ed907618fd6783fc3.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_0bc88fc91219593678543a57d34b0214.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_be050c92794a7f0513dbb7a9624b84a6.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"坂井喜左衛門","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"さかい きざえもん","description":"直の父\n尾張国中村で大きな影響力を持つ土豪。ある事情で藤吉郎を憎んでおり、小一郎が娘の直と親しい関係にあることもよく思っていない。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"D28D652D-14DF-41E4-AF68-C61C5B3274CB","wikidataId":"Q1134047"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"菅田 将暉","detailedNameRuby":"すだ まさき","familyName":"菅田","givenName":"将暉","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"すだ","detailedGivenNameRuby":"まさき","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_e1e3b7b14d6d865d98b8e0