\nやがて庶民の娘から“戦国のファーストレディ”へと昇りつめる。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"00110902-AE66-45F8-B48D-E45DBA3F0CA8","wikidataId":"Q48758750"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"白石 聖","detailedNameRuby":"しらいし せい","familyName":"白石","givenName":"聖","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"しらいし","detailedGivenNameRuby":"せい","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_1baa2df91b7e56ba54ecfb1fc0c04e54.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_3f071e3e5ed5e23b96fa64ecda80c327.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_2bc62bb524ef23de605f03a3a81f1416.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"直","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"なお","description":"小一郎の幼なじみ“初恋のひと”\n小一郎と藤吉郎の故郷である尾張中村の土豪の娘。小一郎と同い年の幼なじみ。男勝りな性格だが、小一郎のことをひそかに慕っている。乱世に翻弄される悲劇のヒロイン。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"0AB5B169-08AF-4793-B060-4E2771CBA976","wikidataId":"Q11671066"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"高橋 努","detailedNameRuby":"たかはし つとむ","familyName":"高橋","givenName":"努","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"たかはし","detailedGivenNameRuby":"つとむ","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_ac54e3823f28798d4c09b72cd0b38eda.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_babe0d64a43162a7d1b95cf957604482.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_4f24d1cb71aeaa50d26714ec9fdb6939.png","width":200,"height":200}},"