2e:["$","$L12","2KVJ881ZPQ",{"content":{"type":"TVEpisode","id":"2KVJ881ZPQ","name":"(6)兄弟の絆(きずな)","detailedEpisodeNameRuby":"","identifierGroup":{"tvEpisodeId":"2KVJ881ZPQ","tvSeriesId":"P52L88MYXY","tvEpisodeName":"(6)兄弟の絆(きずな)","tvSeriesName":"大河ドラマ「豊臣兄弟！」","hashtag":[],"siteId":"8969","serviceId":["g1","g2","s1","s5"],"aliasId":"toyotomi-kyodai","formatGenreTag":[{"id":"03","name":"ドラマ"}],"themeGenreTag":[{"id":"031","name":"国内ドラマ"},{"id":"033","name":"時代劇"},{"id":"030","name":"ドラマ全般"}]},"keyword":[],"description":"大沢（松尾諭）に信長（小栗旬）の暗殺を企てたという疑いがかかった。小一郎（仲野太賀）の機転で、その場での手打ちは免れるが、このままでは鵜沼城に残った藤吉郎（池松壮亮）の命が危ない。翌日までに大沢の無実を証明することになった小一郎は、調査に奔走しつつ、市（宮﨑あおい）に信長への口添えを頼む。だが市はそれを断り、信長のある過去を語って聞かせる。翌日、手詰まりの小一郎は信長の前で驚きの行動に出る。","dateCreated":"2025-12-22T18:40:52+09:00","dateModified":"2026-02-24T11:08:55+09:00","actor":[{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"29D4D7A7-E3F2-4E1F-94CA-046080070DC0","wikidataId":"Q11444506"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"仲野 太賀","detailedNameRuby":"なかの たいが","familyName":"仲野","givenName":"太賀","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"なかの","detailedGivenNameRuby":"たいが","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_bba932486e9715f0c88077bac28a03a5.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_96550216303231facd956bb116caa614.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_20ad70eaeb107b8f431c2d470fdfdeb2.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"小一郎（豊臣秀長）","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"こいちろう（とよとみ ひでなが）","description":"天下人・豊臣秀吉の弟\n登場時の名は小一郎。兄の天下取りをいちずに支え続けた「天下一の補佐役」といわれている。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"D690F0C8-05B8-4A71-9A1E-13B8A756E70D","wikidataId":"Q1058963"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"池松 壮亮","detailedNameRuby":"いけまつ そうすけ","familyName":"池松","givenName":"壮亮","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"いけまつ","detailedGivenNameRuby":"そうすけ","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_92f02688b9bd99a554065cd296d2952f.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_cb1f34b797811ceac6d68d9b83e9b8f7.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_87292aa7be724fb75464ac6a068a68fd.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"藤吉郎（豊臣秀吉）","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"とうきちろう（とよとみ ひでよし）","description":"小一郎を乱世に巻き込んだ野心家の兄\n小一郎の３歳年上の兄。登場時の名は藤吉郎。尾張中村の貧しい農家で生まれ育ったが、主君である戦国武将・織田信長のもとでメキメキと頭角をあらわし、ついには天下統一を果たす。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"04E1F915-FCA1-441E-B5E2-5D60F7FE75D6","wikidataId":"Q11284289"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"浜辺 美波","detailedNameRuby":"はまべ みなみ","familyName":"浜辺","givenName":"美波","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"はまべ","detailedGivenNameRuby":"みなみ","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_18cf0bd1c6f206300d5597fce517f5f8.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_edbfc099c50a27959c381da20788db7c.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_0f5f7e395d69946dd7f47e133e89c342.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"寧々","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"ねね","description":"夫の秀吉とともに天下人への階段を昇りつめる\n豊臣秀吉の正妻。秀吉が関白に就任したのちは北政所（きたのまんどころ）と称される。\n負けず嫌いの性格で、夫の秀吉とともに出世街道を駆け抜ける。\nやがて庶民の娘から“戦国のファーストレディ”へと昇りつめる。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"00110902-AE66-45F8-B48D-E45DBA3F0CA8","wikidataId":"Q48758750"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"白石 聖","detailedNameRuby":"しらいし せい","familyName":"白石","givenName":"聖","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"しらいし","detailedGivenNameRuby":"せい","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_0fe4352bc0ad486cf90ca333d73f6914.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_20e3755feba331ef7b91101e09b2a1a1.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_a970a9a9542b4d85fbc1027e68068415.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"直","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"なお","description":"小一郎の幼なじみ“初恋のひと”\n小一郎と藤吉郎の故郷である尾張中村の土豪の娘。小一郎と同い年の幼なじみ。男勝りな性格だが、小一郎のことをひそかに慕っている。乱世に翻弄される悲劇のヒロイン。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"66D5AA5D-8A64-4B6A-ABB7-5292F551EB64","wikidataId":"Q456644"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"坂井 真紀","detailedNameRuby":"さかい まき","familyName":"坂井","givenName":"真紀","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"さかい","detailedGivenNameRuby":"まき","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_be82055d1422408d4df158e98f8e70e9.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_297fac5c0abd7f590defc6551b0785b1.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_e602af3899bd45ae871f300d77aeb2ae.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"なか","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"","description":"息子たちの出世を温かく見守る母\n豊臣兄弟の母。夫を早くに亡くし、女手一つで二男二女を育てる。息子たちの異例の出世に喜びやとまどいを感じながらも温かく見守り、天下人となった秀吉が関白に就任すると「大政所（おおまんどころ）」と称されるようになる。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"6ABEEFA2-19A4-43EA-925F-33D149C78049","wikidataId":"Q1134063"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"大東 駿介","detailedNameRuby":"だいとう しゅんすけ","familyName":"大東","givenName":"駿介","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"だいとう","detailedGivenNameRuby":"しゅんすけ","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_42b3713df389b68e262cba1c027bdd2e.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_d9f3ba7a1e23be5e48fa46753c5e93e2.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_208aeb567f2eb538f20be52b6e3d7019.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"前田利家","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"まえだ としいえ","description":"秀吉の生涯の友であり出世争いのライバル\n血気盛んで派手好きな「かぶき者」だが、槍（やり）の名手として数々の武功をあげ、秀吉と同世代の良きライバルとして出世争いを繰り広げる。やがて柴田勝家の与力として北陸方面軍の一翼を担うが、信長亡きあと勝家と秀吉が対立することになる。のちに五大老の一人として豊臣政権を支え、加賀百万石と称される加賀藩の礎を築く。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"B51D0BFB-D8F3-44E3-A5D6-FBCE1B54AE30","wikidataId":"Q11529701"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"松尾 諭","detailedNameRuby":"まつお さとる","familyName":"松尾","givenName":"諭","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"まつお","detailedGivenNameRuby":"さとる","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_9dce003847eaf03a94f38327a3af13b7.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_2dfc1a8e34c885397022fce7618ff935.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_d9851c77b75e12a997a8f4ef37c016d6.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"大沢次郎左衛門","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"おおさわ じろうざえもん","description":"美濃の要衝・鵜沼城の城主\n小一郎たちから、織田方に寝返らないかと調略を受ける。礫（つぶて）打ちの名人。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"33A709F5-6B0B-4AC2-A757-3EE61BAEAA68","wikidataId":"Q11467539"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"山口 馬木也","detailedNameRuby":"やまぐち まきや","familyName":"山口","givenName":"馬木也","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"やまぐち","detailedGivenNameRuby":"まきや","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_15931ec1d4d47a797b3f63471e4f8cb1.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_79787545c1c002b53053bdf991bc18bd.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_87776243a43926e281a519ccc036edd0.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"柴田勝家","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"しばた かついえ","description":"兄弟の前に立ちはだかる大きな壁\n織田信長の重臣の一人。勇猛果敢な戦上手で「鬼柴田」の異名で恐れられた。足軽時代の小一郎と藤吉郎にとっては怖くて苦手な存在。やがて二人が出世を果たすとあからさまに毛嫌いするようになる。信長亡きあとの「清須会議」では後継者争いを繰り広げ、やがて「賤ケ岳の戦い」で兄弟と激突することになる。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"DF67D531-44A9-491B-8A45-E373107544BA","wikidataId":"Q253873"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"宮﨑 あおい","detailedNameRuby":"みやざき あおい","familyName":"宮﨑","givenName":"あおい","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"みやざき","detailedGivenNameRuby":"あおい","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_c10ea05d98950386bb1e035c703385fb.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_863cae13c5e3efd46d2bcb715a68650a.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_9c29c4086e33985389330e70402d42d9.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"市","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"いち","description":"波乱の生涯を歩む戦国ヒロイン\n織田信長の妹。乱世に翻弄され悲劇的な一生を送るが、兄・信長と織田家のため波乱万丈な生涯を毅然（きぜん）として生き抜いた戦国ヒロインのひとり。信長と同盟を結ぶ近江の浅井長政に嫁ぎ、茶々・初・江の三姉妹を生み育てるが、のちに兄と夫が対立することになる。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}},{"person":{"identifierGroup":{"npgId":"F8A68291-926B-4D78-92E8-DA8D8B46ABAF","wikidataId":"Q457825"},"roleName":"Actor","displayRoleName":"俳優","name":"小栗 旬","detailedNameRuby":"おぐり しゅん","familyName":"小栗","givenName":"旬","detailedFamilyNameRuby":"おぐり","detailedGivenNameRuby":"しゅん","detailedNameDescription":"","honorificSuffix":"","jobTitle":[],"memberOf":[],"image":{"main":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_67abfcde9f1ca7f00a22417945168442.png","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_0a1e60b5d188f3db10e7dd344d64d75f.png","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_78b15fdd0397ff4e3ccaf14cd51bac26.png","width":200,"height":200}},"characterName":"織田信長","detailedCharacterNameRuby":"おだ のぶなが","description":"天下一統を狙う孤高のカリスマ\n大胆で革新的な戦略と非凡なリーダーシップにより領土を拡大し、「天下布武」のスローガンのもと天下一統を目指したカリスマ的武将。立身出世を目指す小一郎（のちの秀長）と藤吉郎（のちの秀吉）兄弟にとって絶対的な主君である。当主争いで対立した弟を自らの手で殺害したという苦い過去を持っている。","detailedWork":[],"hasOccupation":[]}}],"contributor":[],"partOfSeries":{"id":"P52L88MYXY","name":"大河ドラマ「豊臣兄弟！」","detailedSeriesNameRuby":"とよとみきょうだい","identifierGroup":{"tvSeriesId":"P52L88MYXY","tvSeriesPlaylistId":"series-tep-P52L88MYXY","tvSeriesUId":"p0defc81f-a07b-55e0-b9a6-c7f75720f416","tvSeriesName":"大河ドラマ「豊臣兄弟！」","hashtag":[],"siteId":"8969","serviceId":["g1","g2","s1","s2","s5"],"aliasId":"toyotomi-kyodai","formatGenre":[{"id":"03","name":"ドラマ"}],"nod":{"id":"P202500491700000","url":"https://www.nhk-ondemand.jp/program/P202500491700000/"}},"keyword":["NHK","大河ドラマ","豊臣兄弟！","戦国時代","豊臣秀長","豊臣秀吉","八津弘幸","仲野太賀","池松壮亮","吉岡里帆","浜辺美波","白石聖","坂井真紀","宮澤エマ","大東駿介","松下洸平","山口馬木也","宮﨑あおい","小栗旬"],"detailedSynonym":[],"sameAs":[{"name":"▶︎公式Instagram アカウント","url":"https://www.instagram.com/nhk_toyotomi/"},{"name":"▶︎公式X（旧Twitter）アカウント","url":"https://x.com/nhk_toyotomi"},{"name":"▶︎NHK公式YouTube「豊臣兄弟！」プレイリスト","url":"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcynJ47QaWNvaqX7QpxWQbRs1tHrRHgnb"}],"canonical":"https://www.web.nhk/tv/an/toyotomi-kyodai/pl/series-tep-P52L88MYXY","description":"【NHK公式】大河ドラマ「豊臣兄弟！」\n\n大河ドラマ第65作で描くのは、戦国時代のど真ん中!!\n強い絆で天下統一という偉業を成し遂げた豊臣兄弟の奇跡──\n夢と希望の下剋上（げこくじょう）サクセスストーリーです！\n\n主人公は天下人の弟・豊臣秀長（とよとみ・ひでなが）\n歴史にif（もしも）はないものの…\n\n『秀長が長生きしていれば豊臣家の天下は安泰だった』\n\nとまでいわしめた天下一の補佐役・秀長の目線で戦国時代をダイナミックに描く波乱万丈のエンターテインメント！\n\n【放送予定】\n2026年1月4日（日）スタート ※初回15分拡大版\n\n【作】八津弘幸\n【音楽】木村秀彬\n【語り】安藤サクラ\n【出演】仲野太賀、池松壮亮、吉岡里帆、浜辺美波、白石 聖、坂井真紀、宮澤エマ、菅田将暉、大東駿介、松下洸平、山口馬木也、宮﨑あおい、小栗 旬　ほか\n【時代考証】黒田基樹、柴 裕之\n【制作統括】松川博敬、堀内裕介\n【プロデューサー】高橋優香子、舟橋哲男、吉岡和彦（展開・プロモーション）、国友 茜（広報）\n【演出】渡邊良雄、渡辺哲也、田中 正","detailedCatch":"熱い兄弟が夢と希望を胸に突っ走る奇跡の下剋上サクセスストーリー！","logo":{"main":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-logo_c64ecc100161d9ce85c8aa953bc73ae1.jpg","width":1080,"height":1080},"medium":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-logo_64a636dd72417d3cf661cb2f6808c33a.jpg","width":640,"height":640},"small":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-logo_b696c913daeb18f3a663376fa0ec438b.jpg","width":200,"height":200}},"eyecatch":{"large":{"url":"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-eyec